title: 13 Hours. Official Movie Trailer #2 [HD] (2016)
description:
In theaters: January 15th, 2016

Description:

Based on the book 13 Hours: The Inside Account of What Really Happened in Benghazi.
An American Ambassador is killed during an attack at a U.S. compound in Libya as a security team struggles to make sense out of the chaos.

Director: Michael Bay

Writers: Chuck Hogan, Mitchell Zuckoff

Actors: John Krasinski, Pablo Schreiber, Domicnic Fumusa, Max Martini, James Badge Dale, Toby Stephens, Matt Letscher, David Denman, David Costabile, David Giuntoli

Genre: Drama, Action and Adventure
